# Allowlist style: ignore everything, then unignore what the build needs.
*

!pnpm-workspace.yaml
!pnpm-lock.yaml
!package.json
!SERVICES
!PACKAGES

# Re-ignore heavy or generated content inside the allowed dirs.
**/node_modules
**/dist
**/.turbo
**/.next
**/coverage
**/*.log
**/.env
**/.env.*
!**/.env.example
